Class CareerStaffController

Object
CareerStaffController
All Implemented Interfaces:
ICareerStaffController
public class CareerStaffController extends Object implements ICareerStaffController
Implementation of the ICareerStaffController interface. This controller manages administrative operations for career staff and depends only on the IDataRepo abstraction.
